{"tid":2492080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方去信《蘋果》　不滿將學童參觀國安日活動擬成831太子站事件","createTime":"2021-04-16T22:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T22:49:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"98ab9f25085b598315eb90d751cef2ff4a141769","tid":2492080,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:28:12.000Z","msg":"警察學院於昨日(15日)的全民國家安全教育日開放日中，有小學生被拍攝到模擬在港鐵車廂內，手持仿製膠槍指向同學頭部。警務處處長鄧炳強於今日的立法會財務委員會特別會議上，指斥有報道抹黑學生與「黑暴」有關，晚上警方再在Facebook公布，已發信予《蘋果日報》，指其照片說明「加以扭曲」，手法不道德。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今日以小學生在警察學院用槍指同學的照片為頭版相片，並有圖片說明引網民意見，稱驚訝畫面如「重演」2019年8月31日警察衝入港鐵太子站車廂情況，最後一句質疑警察「到底向下一代教育了甚麼?」<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科向該報總編輯發信，指照片為「一班參與活動的小童開心玩耍」，批評該報「加以扭曲」，與8.31「港鐵太子站發生的事件」連繫，手法並不道德，認為是「借意扭曲」活動原意，感憤怒和遺憾，作出強烈抗議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210415/459460184255762432675312.jpeg/MIbAmuaxBBh2SlbevrQArqb4QEefnsr9lJ3ZFZSd2RU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210415%2F459460184255762432675312.jpeg%2FMIbAmuaxBBh2SlbevrQArqb4QEefnsr9lJ3ZFZSd2RU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=4ebba984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210416/459818260817252352659347.jpeg/A2NSDiI6d8a8ZzZwhUrw5WcrSzt1MT3wmQkbOJkJGzg?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210416%2F459818260817252352659347.jpeg%2FA2NSDiI6d8a8ZzZwhUrw5WcrSzt1MT3wmQkbOJkJGzg%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=f363ab96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource:支那01"},{"pid":"f69b6a0b89c0ae6bc72c4443a9d88ee3934e982f","tid":2492080,"uid":18948,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:30:16.000Z","msg":"根據狗方講法，當日狗隻咩都冇做錯，聯想為831有咩問題"},{"pid":"ad2164b1d0ce98f7bc9ba04f811329ce5a15c53b","tid":2492080,"uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:30:59.000Z","msg":"多謝承認831"},{"pid":"08511150fc28631ee8b0ba58129853a901219d8a","tid":2492080,"uid":56999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:33:06.000Z","msg":"不滿可以去投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0037bc232174ef7b02c02dfe7eb7e104e29aaf","tid":2492080,"uid":70888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:33:18.000Z","msg":"即係黑警都承認 831黑警係黨鐵入面血腥暴力亂打市民？"},{"pid":"c6e541258256f82ea32b3db8bf7c48ff2fe5dffe","tid":2492080,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:35:24.000Z","msg":"既然831「咩都冇發生過」，點解popo又要咁驚人地提？仲要煞有介事安排細路仔入去模擬車廂度拎玩具槍？"},{"pid":"536585e33171c324c3f72946d6840d7f10e93316","tid":2492080,"uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:36:56.000Z","msg":"納粹青年軍都好開心喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPnMaRTJqDC32tYFE5gWLTBMSzPtdsN5MK7FCw6cifJ2U?filename=6WoOCOq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WoOCOq.jpg&h=797975d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcgzFn3geLE4kSHVfXMYcgp2cTL2G4UiEfRSZ3D7odotL?filename=EAzKa8q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAzKa8q.jpg&h=009d0ede&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme1JpYZcAWhZBudQR1WBK6bjoPcVX6HsSZ3i5tKZxEJ1K?filename=p283rGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp283rGL.jpg&h=4d24ded7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaJYbba7eBqrshvJCjDeF1tAPpiTtUqK16rgrTyRLVYWd?filename=BMs7TmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMs7TmL.jpg&h=3eaceca9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48352900cbe00050fc0d56e5f624bc58de2343ac","tid":2492080,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f69b6a0b89c0ae6bc72c4443a9d88ee3934e982